&lt;h3&gt;Support&lt;/h3&gt;
Services are unmanaged however our UK based support team is on hand 24/7 via telephone and the ticket desk should a hardware or network issue need resolving.
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Addons/Extras&lt;/h3&gt;
Addon pricing varies by location, however we can accommodate larger bandwidth requests, additional IP's (subject to justification) and additional cores/resources; for more information contact us.
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Something else...?&lt;/h3&gt;
We offer a range of OpenVZ/KVM Instances and Resource Pools in addition to dedicated servers and development services. Have a project or deployment you need assistance with? Feel free to contact us.
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Billing/Pricing&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Initial purchases may be manually reviewed prior to provisioning, otherwise automated; (&amp;lt;30s typically). All prices exclude VAT. We invoice in GBP.
Residents in the EU will be charged VAT, if you have a EU VAT ID then your charge will be removed. Prices meet $7/m &gt; £ requirements as of 20:44UTC 5/2/2016. PayPal &amp;  BitCoin are enabled for these product ranges.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;strong&gt;If you have any questions or want more information feel free to open a ticket.&lt;/strong&gt;
